Gitdex is my entry for IndexTank and Heroku's holiday search competition. Gitdex has 
a predefined set of interesting github repositories that are fully indexed and searchable
via the IndexTank API.

Gitdex is a Sinatra app that uses Redis and IndexTank for data storage.

Competition details at http://blog.indextank.com/93/holiday-hacks-indextank-heroku/

Gitdex is licensed under the MIT license
